title: Crazy Chicken Pirates
description:
Crazy Chicken Pirates
                              #####################



 An idyllic Caribbean archipelago is infested with Crazy Chicken pirates. It is up to you to restore peace to these shores!

 Raid the island, shoot the enemies and grab as much priceless treasure as you can before time runs out. The crazy chickens will vigorously defend their hideout with cannons and cutlasses before plunging bravely into the waves in their boats for a desperate final counter attack (Bonus Game).

 With lightning-fast gameplay and beautiful scrolling graphics, Crazy Chicken Pirates is a blast!
